\par\pard\plain \fi288\sb240\sl480\slmult1\ql\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Raefe talked to Tosh about saving Nila. They knew that some of the Norcamb bunch had ways to sneak in to New Kendall. But could they get all the way to the Nila\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92s hiding place? They agreed Tosh would bike up to the Norcamb settlement and see if they could help. He was back in an hour, smiling.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93They\u8217\'92ll have her back here before dark. \u8216\'91Piece of pie\u8217\'92 they said. Cheeky lot!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93Nothing wrong with that!\u8221\'94 Raefe said. \u8220\'93I\u8217\'92m just glad we can get her out.\u8221\'94}
